{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc03346cc-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17252"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"17252"},"text":"§ 17252.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Review of large-scale programs","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall enter into an arrangement with the National Academy of Sciences for an independent review and oversight, beginning in 2011, of the programs under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s16293/c"},"text":"section 16293(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":" and under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s17251"},"text":"section 17251 of this title","children":[],"tail":", to ensure that the benefits of such programs are maximized. Not later than "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2012-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 2012","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary shall transmit to the Congress a report on the results of such review and oversight."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc03346cd-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/140/tVII/s704"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–140, title VII, § 704","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2007-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2007","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/121/1709"},"text":"121 Stat. 1709","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/260/dZ/tIV/s4003/c/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–260, div. Z, title IV, § 4003(c)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2020-12-27"},"text":"Dec. 27, 2020","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/2539"},"text":"134 Stat. 2539","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idc03346ce-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"t